ShellSort竊須
    arr竊絶嵯
    n竊絶欧arr
    gap竊絶穴nﾃｷ2
    :While gap>0
        :For i :In gap+竝ｳn-gap
            temp竊紳rr[i]
            j竊進
            :While (j竕･gap)竏ｧ(arr[j-gap]>temp)
                arr[j]竊紳rr[j-gap]
                j竊針-gap
            :EndWhile
            arr[j]竊腎emp
        :EndFor
        gap竊絶穴gapﾃｷ2
    :EndWhile
    arr
}

竡補̯ShellSort 64 34 25 12 22 11 90
